      <title>哈克称美联储需要“开始下调利率”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/harker-says-fed-needs-to-start-moving-rates-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[费城联邦储备银行行长帕特里克·哈克表示，央行应启动降息程序并“继续推进”。哈克在杰克逊霍尔经济研讨会间隙发表了上述讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/harker-says-fed-needs-to-start-moving-rates-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 15:23:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍威尔：杰克逊霍尔研讨会完整演讲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/fed-s-powell-full-speech-at-jackson-hole-symposium-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，美联储现在应该下调关键政策利率，这证实了官员们将开始降低借贷成本的预期。他在怀俄明州杰克逊霍尔举行的美联储年度经济研讨会上发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-23/fed-s-powell-full-speech-at-jackson-hole-symposium-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 15:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔押注 9 月降息，美国国债价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/treasuries-rally-as-powell-locks-in-bets-on-a-september-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆鲍威尔在杰克逊霍尔的讲话巩固了人们对央行下个月降息的预期后，美国国债价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/treasuries-rally-as-powell-locks-in-bets-on-a-september-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英镑兑美元升至两年多以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/pound-hits-strongest-level-in-over-two-years-against-us-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英镑攀升至两年多来的最高水平，进一步推动了英镑在全球范围的上涨，而上涨动力源于市场押注英国央行将比美联储更放松货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/pound-hits-strongest-level-in-over-two-years-against-us-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 14:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔暗示即将降息，黄金价格维持在 2,500 美元以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/gold-extends-gains-as-powell-signals-rate-cuts-are-coming</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔暗示降息时机已到后，金价维持在每盎司 2,500 美元以上。]]></description>
