    <item>
      <title>中国信托银行提出收购要约，台湾银行收购战升温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/taiwan-s-bank-takeover-race-heats-up-with-new-bid-for-shin-kong</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾中信金融控股股份有限公司在争夺新光金控股份有限公司的争夺战中加大了赌注，出价近 40 亿美元收购竞争对手的控股权，以打造台湾最大的金融集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/taiwan-s-bank-takeover-race-heats-up-with-new-bid-for-shin-kong</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 12:48:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博柏利连续 15 年入选富时 100 指数，股价暴跌，近乎终结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/burberry-s-15-year-stay-in-ftse-100-nears-end-after-share-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴宝莉集团 (Burberry Group Plc) 即将退出富时 100 指数，从而结束这家奢侈品制造商在英国蓝筹股指数中长达 15 年的排名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/burberry-s-15-year-stay-in-ftse-100-nears-end-after-share-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 10:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔暗示降息，墨西哥比索引领新兴市场上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席鲍威尔表示调整货币政策的时机已经到来，新兴市场股市和货币随之上涨，带动风险资产上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-23/emerging-markets-set-to-cap-weekly-gains-as-traders-await-powell</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Aug 2024 10:36:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称是时候降息，风险偏好情绪推动油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示现在是降息的时候了，随后油价与风险资产一起上涨，但由于主要经济体的经济前景疲软，油价仍呈周线下跌趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 23:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：标普 500 指数上涨 1%，因“鲍威尔转向”导致债券收益率下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔强化了人们对央行将在 9 月份降息的预期——同时为进一步降息留下空间——之后，股市上涨，债券收益率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 22:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
